overview: Felix is an ordinary high school student who has many interesting friends, but his girlfriend Dasha does not like them. With their friend Mark, they decide to do a prallet with their friends in a house on the outskirts of town, but at one point something goes very wrong. The forest around town is full of special secrets. After that, their lives will never be the same as before. This party may be the last for them. Can they handle the blow of fate or not?
title: Frustration
